Summary: Sighting of star-like steady white glow object at very high altitude in West Vancouver
divs: sighting detailspossible ufo sighting last night 1o\16\2011 - sitting on bench in dundarave boardwalk, very high up, looked like a star, moving n>s for about 4 seconds, then poof, disappeared, as if heading into space, other stars near disappearing point clearly visible. the sky was nearly dark, very easy to distinguish something moving in the sky, it was very high up, looked like it was in space. could not take picture, no camera with me.
